translated: Andersson, Carl-Helge, district fiscal, Grästorp, b. 5/5/97 in Aiboga parish, Älvsborg 1., to Johan R. A. and Anna Charlotta Andersson. M. 26 with Greta Maria Abrahamsson. Children: Tore b. 27, Marianne b. 29, Lennart b. 30, Gunilla b. 36. - Graduate of Skövde realskola and municipal gymnasium, district fiscal in Vänersborg 24. Appointed as a district fiscal in Älvsborg and Stockholm counties 20-27, railway district fiscal in Dal-Västra Värmland's railway construction 25 and 26, interim district fiscal in Ase district 27, regular district fiscal in the same district 32, district fiscal in Grästorps district since 41. Chairman of various income, tax, and property tax boards in Skaraborg 1. since 28, tax consultant since 43, member of the property assessment board, chairman of the municipal assembly and the board for higher elementary schools, deputy chairman of the school board and the building board in Grästorps town, member of the municipal council since 30, member of the municipal executive committee 30-41, chairman of Grästorps rent board since 42, member of the board of the association of district fiscals in Skaraborg county, Skaraborg county shooting association, and Skaraborg county hunting conservation association, chairman of Grästorps shooting guild, member of the board of Vara home guard district, member of the board of building obligation for courthouse in Äse and other district courts, civil defense chief in Grästorps Co, and representative in Ase and Vis'te Härads Savings Bank since 30. Hobbies: hunting, shooting, and voluntary defense movements. Skaraborg county shooting association distinguished: GM, Military Shooting SM, State Shooting Mark, Skiing Mark, and gold shooting badge.
